headline: KKR: The Value Case Is Strong, Despite The Macro Risks (Rating Upgrade)
summary: KKR management reaffirmed 2026 FRE per share guidance of $4.50 but flagged potential market volatility. Read why KKR stock is upgraded to a Buy.
